summary: low contrast scheme, light or dark
name: ChocolatePapaya
description:
This is a unified light/dark version of PapayaWhip (vimscript #591) and ChocolateLiquor (vimscript #592). Both are pretty easy on the eyes, and feature the colors PapayaWhip and one I call ChocolateLiquor (aka #3F1F1F).

Light Version: http://home.ptd.net/~gwilliam/vim/PapayaWhip.png
Dark Version: http://home.ptd.net/~gwilliam/vim/ChocolateLiquor.png
